{"id":656976,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/10/【麻辣总局】天道好轮回-华为饶过谁？/","date":"2020-10-02T08:10:31Z","modified":"2020-10-02T08:10:31Z","title":"【麻辣总局】天道好轮回 华为饶过谁？","content":"<p>10月1日，有网友截图了几条某华为用户的微博消息：2019年12月、2020年4月，这名用户两次怒批其他网友“黑华为”，未料在2020年9月又发消息为自购的“华为折叠屏”手机质量问题而抱怨，成为几个月前自己曾经批过的“黑华为博主”，引得不少网友用原话回呛。</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-656979\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EjPq8OlU4AE5reF.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"433\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EjPq8OlU4AE5reF.jpeg 720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EjPq8OlU4AE5reF-300x216.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-656977\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EjN8_HmXcAAvNLm.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"516\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EjN8_HmXcAAvNLm.jpeg 659w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EjN8_HmXcAAvNLm-291x300.jpeg 291w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-656978\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EjN9BxBX0AE0hwI.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"784\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EjN9BxBX0AE0hwI.jpeg 574w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EjN9BxBX0AE0hwI-191x300.jpeg 191w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>相关阅读：</p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"dkFYrkRlJY\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/09/%e3%80%90%e9%ba%bb%e8%be%a3%e6%80%bb%e5%b1%80%e3%80%91%e7%9f%a5%e4%b9%8e%e7%bd%91%e5%8f%8b%ef%bc%9a%e5%8d%8e%e4%b8%ba%e7%ac%91%e8%af%9d60%e5%88%99/\">【麻辣总局】知乎网友：华为笑话60则</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; cli